# Common Rules

## Analytics Documentation Sync

When any code changes are made to files in `src/analytics/` — check whether the change requires updating `docs/analytics.md`. This includes but is not limited to:

- New methods added to `AnalyticsService`
- Changes to method signatures or behavior
- New event types or property schemas
- Changes to configuration, initialization, or the config resolution flow
- Changes to login/logout detection logic
- New exports or hooks added to the analytics module

If the change affects any documented behavior, API, or architecture, update `docs/analytics.md` to reflect the change before completing the task.
